divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: IT was approsimately 12:30 Am on saterday march 19 2005. I was in my bed almost asleep when I heared a soft ta-ta-ta sound coming from outside my window. When I looked outside and I saw two lites floting side by side blinking at the exactly the same time. I watched it go acrossed the sky for a minute in a very slight u shap headed NorthEast and then in an instant it sharply turned East without stoping and speeded of. It was a clear dark night the Lights where shaped like eyes almost.The ufo was circular and it was a dark shiny color. A few seconds later I heared the same ta-ta-ta sound but when I looked out my window this time I couldn t see enything but by folowing the sound it sounded like it was headed in the same direction. This was at about 12:02am
